facebook/message: Yesterday the Remainers were warning us Brexit would cause World War III. Now they're making out Boris Johnson is Putin's man in Uxbridge. I don't know if it's because we're level in the polls, but they're really getting desperate.Boris Johns...
When the calm and measured @tombradby is saying this, you know Number 10 has stuffed up big time  https://t.co/6Fof3Bc2Cd
I thought @matthew_elliott came over very well this afternoon. Calm, clear, convincing. One or two MPs on committee could learn from him
Boris never mentioned Putin this morning. He rightly pointed out that EU mishandled Ukraine situation. Desperate stuff from Remain
